<pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2017 17:28:22 +0000</pubDate>
<dc:creator>ShiwangiPeswani@TWC</dc:creator>
<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:title>World’s most powerful console, Xbox One X, launches worldwide</og:title>
<og:description>The much talked about and world’s most powerful console, Xbox One X, has launched in 35 markets worldwide today. You get a free game with every purchase.</og:description>
<og:url>http://news.thewindowsclub.com/xbox-one-x-launches-worldwide-news-center-90880/</og:url>
