&lt;p&gt;Next, insert the memory drive on your password-protected PC and wait for the program to load on the home screen. Then, simply choose the Windows version of the computer and the username from the given list. Now, hit the “Reset Password” button and restart your PC.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
