&lt;h3&gt;3: Reset Microsoft Profile Password (Works with Microsoft Account only)&lt;/h3&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;If you have chosen Microsoft account as your account type to protect your PC then you can directly reset the password of your Microsoft account using any computer or smartphone. This works only if you are using an Email and password to enter into your PC otherwise if you are using local accounts then this method is pretty much useless.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Step 1.&lt;/strong&gt; Go to live.com and visit the official forgotten password page. Click on “I Forgot My Password” and continue.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;size-full wp-image-863 aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/windows-password-receovery-6.png&quot; alt=&quot;windows-password-receovery-6&quot; width=&quot;434&quot; height=&quot;472&quot; srcset=&quot;http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/windows-password-receovery-6.png 434w, http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/windows-password-receovery-6-400x435.png 400w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 434px) 100vw, 434px&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Step 2.&lt;/strong&gt; Enter your Email or phone number associated with your Microsoft account.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;size-full wp-image-864 aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/windows-password-receovery-4.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;windows-password-receovery-4&quot; width=&quot;478&quot; height=&quot;608&quot; srcset=&quot;http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/windows-password-receovery-4.jpg 478w, http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/windows-password-receovery-4-400x509.jpg 400w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Step 3.&lt;/strong&gt; Receive the OTP on your recovery email or phone and finally, setup a new password for your MS account.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;size-large wp-image-865 aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/windows-password-receovery-5-600x418.png&quot; alt=&quot;windows-password-receovery-5&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;418&quot; srcset=&quot;http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/windows-password-receovery-5.png 600w, http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/windows-password-receovery-5-400x279.png 400w&quot; sizes=&quot;(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
