<og:title>Bandicam 4.0 is a powerful All in One Recording Software for Windows</og:title>
<og:description>Bandicam is the Recording Software for screen, games &amp; webcam that you want installed on your Windows PC. Read review, buy &amp; download its full version.</og:description>
<og:url>http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/bandicam-4-0-review</og:url>
