<pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2017 16:59:07 +0000</pubDate>
<dc:creator>ShiwangiPeswani@TWC</dc:creator>
<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:title>Over-the-Cable Updater Tool for Windows Mobile 10 released</og:title>
<og:description>Windows Phone users can now update their Windows Phone devices using their Windows 10 PC with the newly released Over-the-Cable Updater Tool.</og:description>
<og:url>http://news.thewindowsclub.com/over-the-cable-updater-tool-for-windows-mobile-10-90860/</og:url>
<og:image>http://news.thewindowsclubco.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Windows-10-Mobile-nypd.jpg</og:image>
