&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy to Operate&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;For the first download, the software will download the analyzer so that the video that you are about to download can be analyzed. The button with plus sign in the extreme left is there to add YouTube video link. You can add, copy and paste the video link from YouTube and the downloader will start analyzing all the possible options. Now, this is up to you to decide the format, the resolution and size of the video. The downloader cannot offer more than the maximum available option with the original video. Check below to find how the analyser works and what options are available to you.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
