&lt;p&gt;One of the most exciting features of WinX YouTube downloader is that you can download multiple videos at the same time. All you need to do is to add videos following the same direction for all the videos that need to be downloaded and then click the download button. You can also stop download in between if you feel a video is not needed or you are out of internet connection. Apart from downloading, you can also choose to convert the video to the format you like and that can be done with a single click if you have already downloaded the converter.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Changeable settings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
