<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:title>CloudBerry Backup Ultimate: Best Solution to Backup Business Data</og:title>
<og:description>ColudBerry Backup Ultimate Edition for Windows, Mac, Linux offers administrators a single backup solution to cover entire data landscape be it cloud or local.</og:description>
<og:url>http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/cloudberry-backup-ultimate-business-review</og:url>
<og:image>http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/CloudBerry-backup-1.png</og:image>
<dc:language>en-US</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
<dc:identifier>http://reviews.thewindowsclub.com/cloudberry-backup-ultimate-business-review</dc:identifier>
